## Context

- Automatically correct TypeScript and ESLint errors to ensure clean code before deployment.

## Workflow

1. Run `pnpm lint` to check for linting issues.
2. Correct all errors and re-run `pnpm lint` until no errors remain.
3. Run `pnpm ts` to check for TypeScript issues.
4. Correct all errors and re-run `pnpm ts` until no errors remain.